instruction:
已知信息：
'（四）有与生产的化妆品品种、数量和生产许可项目等相适应的技术人员；'可被翻译为：(4) having technicians who are suited to the varieties, quantity and manufacturing licensed items, etc. of the cosmetics manufactured;
'（二）有与生产的化妆品品种、数量和生产许可项目等相适应的生产场地，且与有毒、有害场所以及其他污染源保持规定的距离；'可被翻译为：(2) having the manufacturing premises that are appropriate to the varieties, quantity and manufacturing licensed items, etc. of the cosmetics produced, and being kept prescribed distance from toxic and hazardous premises and other sources of pollution;
'（五）有与生产的化妆品品种、数量相适应，能对生产的化妆品进行检验的检验人员和检验设备；'可被翻译为：(5) having the staff members and equipment that are appropriate to the varieties and quantity of the cosmetics produced and that can perform inspection of the cosmetics produced;
'第四十六条 为降低污染和交叉污染的风险，厂房、生产设施和设备应当根据所生产药品的特性、工艺流程及相应洁净度级别要求合理设计、布局和使用，并符合下列要求：'可被翻译为：Article 46: In order to minimize the risks of contamination and cross-contamination, premises, facilities and equipment should be designed, laid out and used appropriately in accordance with the properties of the manufactured product and its process, as well as the corresponding cleanliness level, and the following requirements should be met:

根据上述已知信息，请将'（三）有与生产的化妆品品种、数量和生产许可项目等相适应的生产设施设备且布局合理，空气净化、水处理等设施设备符合规定要求；'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'第十四条 医疗器械生产企业按照本办法第十条、第十二条的要求进行调查评估后，确定医疗器械产品存在缺陷的，应当立即决定并实施召回，同时向社会发布产品召回信息。'可被翻译为：Article 14 After the medical device manufacturer carries out an investigation and assessment in accordance with the requirements of Articles 10 and 12 of these Provisions, if it is confirmed that the medical device product is defective, it shall immediately decide and implement a recall, and disclose the product recall information to the society.
'医疗器械生产企业应当按照食品药品监督管理部门的要求进行召回，并按本办法第十四条第二款的规定向社会公布产品召回信息。'可被翻译为：The medical device manufacturer shall recall in accordance with the requirements of the food and drug regulatory department, and disclose the product recall information to the society in accordance with Paragraph 2, Article 14 of these Provisions.
'（一）未按照本办法规定建立医疗器械召回管理制度的；'可被翻译为：(1) fail to establish a medical device recall management system in accordance with these Provisions;
'（三）违反本办法第十八条、第二十三条、第二十七条第二款规定，未按照食品药品监督管理部门要求采取改正措施或者重新召回医疗器械的；'可被翻译为：(3) fail to take corrective measures or make another round of medical devices recall according to the requirements of the food and drug regulatory department, which violates Article 18, Article 23, and Paragraph 2 of Article 27 of these Provisions;

根据上述已知信息，请将'（一）违反本办法第十四条规定，未按照要求及时向社会发布产品召回信息的；'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'（一）主动申请注销的；'可被翻译为：(1) the cancellation is applied voluntarily;
'（一）主动申请注销药品生产许可证的；'可被翻译为：(1) An application for the revocation of the Drug Manufacturing Certificate is voluntarily submitted;
'第四十二条 已经注册的产品不再生产或者进口的，注册人应当主动申请注销注册证。'可被翻译为：Article 42 If the registered product is no longer produced or imported, the registrant shall take the initiative to apply for cancellation of the registration license.
'化妆品生产企业申请注销生产许可时，原发证的药品监督管理部门发现注销可能影响案件查处的，可以暂停办理注销手续。'可被翻译为：When the cosmetics manufacturer applies for cancelling the cosmetics manufacturing license, if the drug regulatory department issued former license finds out that cancellation may affect investigation of cases, it may suspend handling of the cancellation procedures.

根据上述已知信息，请将'（一）企业主动申请注销的；'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'利用同位素标记的与未标记的抗原或抗体与抗体或抗原发生竞争性抑制反应来测定抗体或抗原含量的方法。'可被翻译为：A method of determining antibody or antigen content using a competitive inhibition reaction between an isotopically labeled antigen or antibody and an unlabeled antigen or antibody.
'1.与致病性病原体抗原、抗体以及核酸等检测相关的试剂；'可被翻译为：1. Reagents related to the testing of antigen, antibody and nucleic acid, etc. for pathogen.
'（一）药品生产场地管理文件以及变更材料；'可被翻译为：(1) site master files and the materials in connection with any change;
'（一）产品所用原辅料的所有变更，尤其是来自新供应商的原辅料；'可被翻译为：1. All changes of starting materials used for the product, especially those materials from new suppliers;

根据上述已知信息，请将'（一）抗原、抗体等主要材料供应商变更的；'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'（三）持有人药品注册证书、药品生产许可证等行政许可被依法吊销或者撤销的；'可被翻译为：(3) Where the MAH's Drug Approval License, Drug Manufacturing Certificate and other administrative licenses have been revoked or withdrawn in accordance with the law;
'（四）药品生产许可证依法被吊销或者撤销的；'可被翻译为：(4) The Drug Manufacturing Certificate has been withdrawn or cancelled according to law;
'（三）营业执照依法被吊销或者注销的；'可被翻译为：(3) The business license has been withdrawn or cancelled according to law;
'（三）被药品监督管理部门依法作出吊销许可证、责令停产停业等处罚的；'可被翻译为：(3) those who receive the punishments such as revoking license or ordering suspension of manufacturing and operation, etc. from the drug regulatory department;

根据上述已知信息，请将'（三）《药品生产许可证》被依法吊销或者缴销的；'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'（八）企业产品抽检、监督检查、投诉举报等发现问题的整改落实情况；'可被翻译为：(8) rectification implementation condition of problems discovered from sample testing of the enterprise’s products, supervision and inspection, complaint report, etc.;
'（二）药品生产企业接受监督检查及整改落实情况；'可被翻译为：(2) information on the inspections that have been made to the drug manufacturer and the conduction of corrective actions;
'第五十八条  药品监督管理部门应当根据监督检查、产品抽检、不良事件监测、投诉举报、行政处罚等情况，定期开展风险会商研判，做好医疗器械质量安全隐患排查和防控处置工作。'可被翻译为：Article 58 The drug regulatory departments shall, in accordance with the conditions of supervision and inspection, sample testing of products, monitoring of adverse events, complaint reporting and administrative penalty, etc., carry out risk analysis and assessment through consultation regularly, and make proper investigation and prevention and control of potential medical device quality and safety hazards.
'跟踪检查可以对企业提交的整改报告进行书面审查，也可以对企业的问题整改、责任落实、纠正预防措施等进行现场复查。'可被翻译为：Follow-up inspection could make written review of the rectification report submitted by the enterprise, or make on-site review of the enterprise’s rectification of problems, implementation of responsibilities, and corrective and preventive measures, etc.

根据上述已知信息，请将'（六）企业产品抽检、监督检查、投诉举报等发现问题的整改落实情况；'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'第十八条 药品生产、经营企业和医疗机构应当建立并保存药品不良反应报告和监测档案。'可被翻译为：Article 18 Drug manufacturers, distributors and medical institutions shall establish and maintain archives for ADR reporting and monitoring.
'（二）未按照规定每年对直接接触药品的工作人员进行健康检查并建立健康档案；'可被翻译为：(2) failing to carry out health examination of personnel in direct contact with drugs each year and establish health achieves; or
'（四）未按照规定进行药品不良反应监测的；'可被翻译为：(4) the adverse drug reaction monitoring is not conducted in accordance with regulations;
'（二）接收或者购进疫苗时未按照规定索取并保存相关证明文件、温度监测记录；'可被翻译为：(2) failing to obtain and keep relevant certification documents and temperature monitoring records when receiving or purchasing vaccines;

根据上述已知信息，请将'（二）未建立和保存药品不良反应监测档案的；'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'（三）三级召回：使用该医疗器械引起危害的可能性较小但仍需要召回的。'可被翻译为：(3) Class III recalls: the use of the medical device is less likely to cause hazard but the device still needs to be recalled.
'（一）一级召回：使用该药品可能引起严重健康危害的;'可被翻译为：(Ⅰ)  Class 1 recall: Use of the drug may cause serious harms to health;
'（二）二级召回：使用该药品可能引起暂时的或者可逆的健康危害的;'可被翻译为：(Ⅱ)  Class 2 recall: Use of the drug may cause temporary or reversible harms to health;
'（一）一级召回：使用该医疗器械可能或者已经引起严重健康危害的；'可被翻译为：(1) Class I recalls: the use of the medical device may cause or has caused serious hazards to health;

根据上述已知信息，请将'（三）三级召回：使用该药品一般不会引起健康危害，但由于其他原因需要收回的。'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'第一百三十六条 国家药品标准，是指国家食品药品监督管理局颁布的《中华人民共和国药典》、药品注册标准和其他药品标准，其内容包括质量指标、检验方法以及生产工艺等技术要求。'可被翻译为：Article 136 National drug standards refer to the Pharmacopoeia of the People's Republic of China, drug registration specifications, etc. published by the State Food and Drug Administration, including the technical requirements such as specifications, testing methods and manufacturing processes, etc.
'（四）产品原液、半成品和成品的检验项目、检验方法和结果是否符合国家药品标准和药品注册标准的要求；'可被翻译为：(IV)  Whether the testing items, testing methods and results of bulk, final bulk and finished products meet the requirements stipulated by national drug standards and drug registration standards;
'（四）产品原液、半成品和成品的检验项目、检验方法和结果是否符合药典和药品注册标准的要求；'可被翻译为：(IV) Whether the testing items, testing methods and results of bulk, final bulk and finished products meet the requirements stipulated by the ChP and the drug registration specifications;
'2.出厂及货架期的中、英文药品标准，检验方法及相关检验方法的方法学验证资料（包括符合现行《中国药典》要求的无菌及微生物限度检查的验证资料），按照现行版《中国药典》格式整理的药品标准及起草说明。'可被翻译为：2.Drug substance release or shelf-life specifications in Chinese and English versions, test methods and relevant method validation data (including validation data for sterility and microbial limit tests in accordance with the current Chinese Pharmacopoeia), specifications and drafting instructions collated as per the format of the current Chinese Pharmacopoeia.

根据上述已知信息，请将'第一百三十七条 药品注册标准的项目及其检验方法的设定，应当符合中国药典的基本要求、国家食品药品监督管理局发布的技术指导原则及国家药品标准编写原则。'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'（一）存放于标志明显的专用场所，并有效隔离，不得销售；'可被翻译为：(I) Such drugs shall be stored in special places clearly marked and effectively isolated, and shall not be sold;
'（一）按剂型、用途以及储存要求分类陈列，并设置醒目标志，类别标签字迹清晰、放置准确。'可被翻译为：(I) Adopting classified display according to the dosage form, indications and storage requirements, and setting up clear marks with legible labels and accurate placement;
'第七十五条 收货人员对符合收货要求的药品，应当按品种特性要求放于相应待验区域，或者设置状态标志，通知验收。冷藏、冷冻药品应当在冷库内待验。'可被翻译为：Article 75 For drugs conforming to receipt requirements, the receiving personnel shall place them in the corresponding area for quarantine according to the characteristics and requirements of the varieties, or set status identification, and notify relevant personnel for acceptance inspection. The refrigerated and frozen drugs shall be placed in the freezer for quarantine.
'（十）经营特殊管理的药品有符合国家规定的储存设施。'可被翻译为：(X) There shall be storage facilities conforming to national provisions for the drugs under special management.

根据上述已知信息，请将'（十）经营非药品应当设置专区，与药品区域明显隔离，并有醒目标志。'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'配制记录、分发与返还记录等完整；'可被翻译为：Records of formulating, distribution, and return, etc. of the test/control articles should be complete;
'1.受试物/对照品的接收、保存、分发、使用、留样、返还或废弃等应有完整记录且数量吻合；'可被翻译为：1. The receipt, storage, distribution, use, reserve samples, return or disposal of the test/control articles should be recorded completely and their accountability should be maintained;
'(1)研究所需实验系统的来源应清晰合规，应完整保存 实验系统购入(转入)、质量鉴定等相关证明性文件；应完整保留适用性评估资料。'可被翻译为：(1) The source of the test system used in the study should be clear and compliant with the related regulation, and the relevant supporting documentation for acquisition and characterization of the test system should be kept completely; documentation for assessing suitability of the test system should be kept completely.
'2.应完整保留研究期间所使用仪器设备的使用、清洁、 保养、测试、校准、确认或验证、维修、异常情况处理、报废等记录；仪器设备使用记录的时间及内容应与研究对应一致；'可被翻译为：2. Records of use, cleaning, maintenance, testing, calibration, verification or validation, repair, handling of unexpected events and decommission of instruments and equipment used in the study during the study period should be retained completely; the testing time and items in the use records of instruments and equipment should be in line with that as required by the study;

根据上述已知信息，请将'4.应完整保留研究所需毒麻药品、造模试剂(药品)等的配制、保存、使用、返还或废弃等记录。'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'在新药审批期间，其注册分类和技术要求不因国内药品生产企业申报的相同活性成份的制剂在我国获准上市而发生变化。'可被翻译为：In the process of the review and approval of a new drug, the registration classification and technical requirements thereof shall not be changed, even though the preparations of the same active ingredients applied for by domestic manufacturers are approved for marketing in China.
'（七）药品上市申请审评审批期间，药品注册分类和技术要求不因相同活性成份的制剂在境内外获准上市而发生变化。药品注册分类在提出上市申请时确定。'可被翻译为：(7) During the review and approval of the drug marketing application, the drug registration classification and technical requirements shall not be changed because the preparation with the same active ingredients is approved to be marketed at home and abroad. Drug registration classification shall be determined when marketing authorization is applied.
'（二）新药生产：150日；获准进入特殊审批程序的品种：120日；'可被翻译为：(2) new drug application for production: 150 days; any drug permitted to enter the special review and approval procedures: 120 days;
'（一）新药临床试验：90日；获准进入特殊审批程序的品种：80日；'可被翻译为：(1) new drug application for clinical trial: 90 days; any drug permitted to enter the special review and approval procedures: 80 days;

根据上述已知信息，请将'第四十八条 在新药审批期间，新药的注册分类和技术要求不因相同活性成份的制剂在国外获准上市而发生变化。'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'申请人、备案人对资料的真实性负责。'可被翻译为：The applicant and filing entity shall take full responsibility for the authenticity of the documents submitted.
'申请人应当对其申请材料全部内容的真实性负责。'可被翻译为：The applicant shall be responsible for the authenticity of all information on the materials for application.
'（四）对申报资料真实性有疑问的；'可被翻译为：(iv) There are doubts about the authenticity of the dossier;
'（六）药品注册过程中认为申报资料不真实，申请人不能证明其真实性的；'可被翻译为：(6) During the drug registration process, the application dossier is considered untruthful, and the applicant cannot prove the authenticity thereof;

根据上述已知信息，请将'申请人应当对申报资料的真实性负责。'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'（七）确保相关信息及其纠正和预防措施已通过高层管理人员的评审。'可被翻译为：7. To ensure that the related information and its CAPA pass the review by the senior management.
'（三）确定所需采取的纠正和预防措施，防止问题的再次发生。'可被翻译为：3. To determine necessary CAPA measures for preventing issues from re-occurring;
'第三十七条  医疗器械注册人、备案人、受托生产企业应当建立纠正措施程序，确定产生问题的原因，采取有效措施，防止相关问题再次发生。'可被翻译为：Article 37 The registrant, filing entity or contract manufacturer of medical devices shall establish procedures for corrective actions, determine the cause for problems and take effective measures, to prevent recurrence of related problems.
'（六）有信息提示相应产品的质量或者质量控制可能存在潜在风险的；'可被翻译为：(VI) There is information suggesting that the quality of the corresponding product or quality control has potential risks;

根据上述已知信息，请将'（六）确保相关信息已传递到质量受权人和预防问题再次发生的直接负责人。'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'3.采用《中华人民共和国药典》及其他法定标准未收载的检验方法；'可被翻译为：3) Testing method adopted is not included in the Chinese Pharmacopoeia or other official standards;
'超出标准(限度)'可被翻译为：OOS: Out of Specification
'4.所有中间控制方法及标准；'可被翻译为：4) The instructions for any in-process controls with their limits;
'提供检验及方法学验证所涉及的标准物质（对照品或标准品），应提供三倍量，以满足标准复核检验及首次进口检验。'可被翻译为：The standard substance (reference or standard product) involved in the test and method validation shall  be provided in triplication to satisfy the standard verification and inspection and initial import inspection.

根据上述已知信息，请将'检验结果超出法定标准及企业制定标准的所有情形。'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

已知信息：
'（七）药品与非药品、外用药与其他药品分开存放，中药材和中药饮片分库存放；'可被翻译为：(VII) Drugs and non-drugs, drugs for topical use and other drugs shall be stored separately, and Chinese crude drugs and Prepared Slices shall be stored separately;
'文件应当分类存放，便于查阅。'可被翻译为：Documents should be laid out by categories and be easy to check.
'第一百五十六条 文件应当分类存放、条理分明，便于查阅。'可被翻译为：Article 156: Documents should be laid out in an orderly fashion and be easy to check.
'（三）经营中药饮片的，有存放饮片和处方调配的设备；'可被翻译为：(III) Those distributing Prepared Slices shall have equipment for storing such drugs and prescription dispensing;

根据上述已知信息，请将'医疗机构应当将药品与非药品分开存放；中药材、中药饮片、化学药品、中成药应分别储存、分类存放。'翻译为英文，只能输出翻译后的句子，不允许添加编造成分。

